    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="operate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Bendix Automatic Drain Valve (DV-2)</title>
        <para>When the key switch is placed in the start or ignition position, power is fed to circuit 39A, (then to an
            inline connector and circuit 39A with a pyrometer only), then to a 15 amp inline fuse, circuit 39B,
            connector (13), circuit 39B, and an inline single connector to the heated drain valve.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
